    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fastener similar to a bolt but with a fine thread and a slotted head for use with a screwdriver. Often used to join sheet metal parts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
